snippet.title: CookieRun: The Darkest Night ~ Chapter 1 ~ Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
An epic VR Action Adventure, 'CookieRun: The Darkest Night' is available for Pre-order!
Pre-order now and receive a 12% discount on the Meta Quest Store!
https://www.meta.com/experiences/5240965299324322

You will play as a not-so-brave cookie named GingerBrave, must find the courage to battle his enemies and solve puzzles to grow into the courageous leader he was destined to be. Along the way, he meets a color cast of ally cookies to help him on this journey.

Step into the immersive world of CookieRun and experience life from a unique perspective – that of a small, freshly baked Cookie. Your journey starts with a daring escape from an oven, setting the stage for an epic adventure.

Visit freshdoh.studio and subscribe for all the latest! https://freshdoh.studio/

Follow us on Instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/studiofreshdoh/
Follow us on Facebook here: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61551449215926 
Follow us on Twitter here: https://twitter.com/studiofreshdoh

쿠키런의 몰입감 넘치는 세계로 들어가 갓 구워진 작은 쿠키의 특별한 삶을 경험해 보세요. 용감한 쿠키가 뜨거운 오븐에서 대담하게 탈출하는 것으로 위대한 모험이 시작됩니다!

플레이어는 그다지 용감하지 못한 '용감한 쿠키'가 되어, 다양한 적과 싸우고 퍼즐을 해결하면서 전설 속의 영웅으로 성장해나가야 합니다. 다양한 쿠키들과 조력자들을 만나 함께 탐험하고, 마녀의 성을 탈출하는 그때까지!

#CookieRun #TheDarkestNight #GingerBrave #CVR #VR #Meta #Quest3 #Adventure
